                Army ROTC
              


















The Fire Battalion is an Army ROTC program in the city of Chicago, with headquarters at the University of Illinois at Chicago and students at nine other colleges and universities. As a Cadet in Army ROTC, you will test your limits and learn what it means to be an officer in the United States Army.








